As the hike in the price of diesel bite harder, singer, Paul Okoye, has lamented spending N1.4 million on diesel to power his house.
Via his Instagram Story, he said, “Ordinary house, I’m spending 1.4m Naira for diesel (Generator and diesel.)”
The price of diesel has been on the rise in recent times due to the ongoing war in Ukraine. The situation is worsened in Nigeria by the collapse of the national grid.
 
